Twitch will start giving Twitch Prime subscribers a collection of free games every month. The company will begin distributing free games to subscribers from 15 March, with first batch including Superhot and Oxenfree. “We’re also happy to announce that all eight titles from Indie Amplifier will be made available for free over the next few months,” said Twitch. The first Indie Amplifier titles available will be Shadow Tactics and Candlekeep: Tomb of Annihilation. The free titles for March include: